1
00:00:10,960 --> 00:00:13,420
♪The maple mark on your skin♪

2
00:00:14,230 --> 00:00:17,040
♪The only proof we exist♪

3
00:00:18,210 --> 00:00:21,450
♪I stole you back from destiny♪

4
00:00:21,560 --> 00:00:24,430
♪But can I redeem myself♪

5
00:00:24,430 --> 00:00:26,540
♪I don't care what fate foretells♪

6
00:00:26,750 --> 00:00:30,330
♪Or how rough the road may be♪

7
00:00:30,340 --> 00:00:33,280
♪Stay, I'll fight for you♪

8
00:00:33,610 --> 00:00:37,660
♪That's all I'll ever do♪

9
00:00:37,760 --> 00:00:39,890
♪If life is just a show♪

10
00:00:39,890 --> 00:00:42,650
♪I'll stay with you till the end♪

11
00:00:42,650 --> 00:00:44,980
♪I'm scared we'll wake up alone♪

12
00:00:44,980 --> 00:00:47,960
♪So don't let this dream end♪

13
00:00:47,960 --> 00:00:52,420
♪In my bones, in my heart♪

14
00:00:52,420 --> 00:00:54,100
♪I know I'll have to leave♪

15
00:00:54,100 --> 00:00:55,670
♪You must not leave my side♪

16
00:00:55,670 --> 00:00:57,260
♪No place can hold us in♪

17
00:00:57,260 --> 00:01:01,910
♪Not when it's you and me♪

18
00:01:06,890 --> 00:01:10,400
♪Forever♪

19
00:01:11,490 --> 00:01:15,250
♪In my soul♪

20
00:01:17,260 --> 00:01:23,300
=This Palace Maid Isn't Very Calm=
=Episode 16=

21
00:01:23,790 --> 00:01:25,350
Greetings, Your Majesty.

22
00:01:25,350 --> 00:01:26,560
Sit down.

23
00:01:26,760 --> 00:01:27,840
Thank you, Your Majesty.

24
00:01:31,150 --> 00:01:33,950
The eunuch who went out to
buy supplies said

25
00:01:34,350 --> 00:01:36,310
that smallpox has appeared
outside the palace.

26
00:01:36,640 --> 00:01:38,400
They said displaced people
entered the capital

27
00:01:38,710 --> 00:01:41,070
and brought smallpox into the capital.

28
00:01:41,510 --> 00:01:44,710
Now the whole capital
is gripped with fear.

29
00:01:45,150 --> 00:01:47,790
Your Majesty, what should we do?

30
00:01:48,590 --> 00:01:51,200
You run the harem now.

31
00:01:51,560 --> 00:01:53,000
What's your plan?

32
00:01:53,950 --> 00:01:55,070
How about

33
00:01:55,640 --> 00:01:58,400
Your Majesty and His Majesty

34
00:01:58,400 --> 00:02:00,070
move to the temporary palace
to avoid smallpox?

35
00:02:00,150 --> 00:02:02,480
If I leave with His Majesty,

36
00:02:02,590 --> 00:02:05,000
what of you consorts in the palace?

37
00:02:05,150 --> 00:02:07,350
We'll stay here.

38
00:02:09,710 --> 00:02:10,800
Enough.

39
00:02:10,800 --> 00:02:13,520
Don't think I can't see your scheme.

40
00:02:13,680 --> 00:02:15,190
I've heard these rumors

41
00:02:15,190 --> 00:02:16,710
in the capital.

42
00:02:16,800 --> 00:02:19,000
But rumors are just rumors.

43
00:02:19,000 --> 00:02:20,190
Unconfirmed.

44
00:02:20,190 --> 00:02:21,190
Don't take it seriously.

45
00:02:21,590 --> 00:02:24,960
If we flee to the temporary palace
at every sign,

46
00:02:25,310 --> 00:02:27,870
where would His Majesty's authority be?

47
00:02:28,310 --> 00:02:29,590
But what if it is true?

48
00:02:29,960 --> 00:02:31,280
If it is true,

49
00:02:31,280 --> 00:02:33,360
we can go to the temporary palace then.

50
00:02:33,750 --> 00:02:37,360
But now the palace is full of rumors,

51
00:02:37,560 --> 00:02:38,680
and everyone is uneasy.

52
00:02:42,470 --> 00:02:43,710
Since you know they are rumors,

53
00:02:43,710 --> 00:02:45,190
you should not let them spread.

54
00:02:45,360 --> 00:02:47,190
You failed to keep the palace in order.

55
00:02:48,560 --> 00:02:49,750
Deliver my order.

56
00:02:49,960 --> 00:02:52,800
From today on,
strengthen palace security.

57
00:02:52,810 --> 00:02:54,280
Strictly check everyone in and out.

58
00:02:54,590 --> 00:02:56,680
Report anyone suspicious immediately

59
00:02:56,750 --> 00:02:58,400
and isolate them.

60
00:02:58,960 --> 00:03:00,630
Yes, Your Majesty.

61
00:03:08,630 --> 00:03:09,470
Your Highness.

62
00:03:12,030 --> 00:03:13,800
Your Highness,
stay in the palace to rest

63
00:03:13,800 --> 00:03:15,120
if you have nothing to do recently,

64
00:03:15,190 --> 00:03:16,190
and don't go out often.

65
00:03:17,280 --> 00:03:19,710
You came back later than usual today.

66
00:03:19,750 --> 00:03:20,960
Did something happen?

67
00:03:20,960 --> 00:03:22,360
I went out to handle affairs today

68
00:03:22,520 --> 00:03:24,710
and found palace security
is much stricter.

69
00:03:24,710 --> 00:03:27,080
The patrolling imperial guards
are several times more than before.

70
00:03:27,080 --> 00:03:28,280
I asked around,

71
00:03:29,120 --> 00:03:30,150
and was told that

72
00:03:30,700 --> 00:03:32,120
someone in the capital has smallpox.

73
00:03:33,150 --> 00:03:34,520
Rumors like that

74
00:03:34,520 --> 00:03:36,000
surface every few years.

75
00:03:36,280 --> 00:03:37,120
Without solid proof,

76
00:03:37,210 --> 00:03:38,150
no need to believe.

77
00:03:38,280 --> 00:03:40,520
But this time, it may be true.

78
00:04:07,960 --> 00:04:09,120
What's wrong with my face?

79
00:04:10,870 --> 00:04:11,710
Zhen'er,

80
00:04:12,800 --> 00:04:13,710
bring me a mirror.

81
00:04:13,870 --> 00:04:14,710
Your Ladyship...

82
00:04:15,280 --> 00:04:16,120
Hurry.

83
00:04:16,480 --> 00:04:17,600
Bring me a mirror.

84
00:04:31,270 --> 00:04:32,110
How can this be?

85
00:04:34,160 --> 00:04:36,120
Why are there so many on my face?

86
00:04:46,160 --> 00:04:47,000
I...

87
00:04:47,040 --> 00:04:48,600
I will go fetch the Imperial Physician
at once.

88
00:04:48,600 --> 00:04:49,440
Stop!

89
00:04:52,480 --> 00:04:53,320
No.

90
00:04:54,500 --> 00:04:55,600
Do not fetch the physician.

91
00:04:59,800 --> 00:05:00,920
But, Your Ladyship...

92
00:05:03,920 --> 00:05:05,070
In the palace,

93
00:05:05,360 --> 00:05:07,270
there has not yet been
a case of smallpox.

94
00:05:07,680 --> 00:05:09,750
If I am the first to be infected,

95
00:05:10,870 --> 00:05:13,600
once word spreads through the palace,

96
00:05:13,950 --> 00:05:15,720
I will be

97
00:05:16,270 --> 00:05:17,830
a sinner in the His Majesty's eyes.

98
00:05:18,950 --> 00:05:20,600
I cannot be the first.

99
00:05:20,600 --> 00:05:22,070
But this illness cannot be delayed.

100
00:05:25,040 --> 00:05:28,070
Your Ladyship, you are not alone now.

101
00:05:28,310 --> 00:05:30,600
You must think of
the imperial heir in your belly.

102
00:05:30,870 --> 00:05:34,160
I am doing this for
the imperial heir in my belly.

103
00:05:38,190 --> 00:05:39,220
This illness

104
00:05:40,040 --> 00:05:41,870
cannot be cured at all.

105
00:05:43,000 --> 00:05:44,160
Survival

106
00:05:45,160 --> 00:05:46,950
depends entirely on fate.

107
00:05:47,750 --> 00:05:49,190
If fate is kind,

108
00:05:49,870 --> 00:05:51,240
we both live.

109
00:05:52,950 --> 00:05:54,720
If fate is cruel,

110
00:05:57,070 --> 00:05:58,560
two lives will be lost.

111
00:06:01,000 --> 00:06:02,360
My child and I

112
00:06:02,950 --> 00:06:04,600
will both die.

113
00:06:05,870 --> 00:06:07,160
At this point,

114
00:06:07,720 --> 00:06:08,950
I can't care about anything else.

115
00:06:10,800 --> 00:06:12,040
Good Zhen'er,

116
00:06:12,800 --> 00:06:14,240
later,

117
00:06:14,240 --> 00:06:15,750
go fetch some rouge and face powder

118
00:06:16,630 --> 00:06:18,270
and help cover this up for me.

119
00:06:19,480 --> 00:06:23,160
No one must find out about this.

120
00:06:24,560 --> 00:06:25,830
And then,

121
00:06:26,510 --> 00:06:27,830
you go to my manor,

122
00:06:28,270 --> 00:06:30,800
send a message to my mother and father,

123
00:06:30,800 --> 00:06:34,270
and tell them to find folk medicine.

124
00:06:35,720 --> 00:06:38,390
This illness is common
among common people,

125
00:06:40,310 --> 00:06:43,390
and palace medicine may not
be better than folk medicine.

126
00:06:45,560 --> 00:06:46,400
Hurry.

127
00:06:48,950 --> 00:06:49,800
Yes.

128
00:06:56,630 --> 00:06:58,920
Any movement in Consort Duan's palace?

129
00:06:59,680 --> 00:07:01,870
Everything is normal so far.

130
00:07:02,560 --> 00:07:04,000
That should not be.

131
00:07:05,390 --> 00:07:06,480
Greetings, Your Ladyship.

132
00:07:06,950 --> 00:07:07,790
No need.

133
00:07:08,720 --> 00:07:10,390
Your Ladyship, bad news.

134
00:07:10,390 --> 00:07:11,230
Something is wrong!

135
00:07:11,360 --> 00:07:13,070
What is it? Why are you so flustered?

136
00:07:13,190 --> 00:07:14,310
It is Consort Duan.

137
00:07:14,630 --> 00:07:16,560
Her personal maid Zhen'er
returned to the palace,

138
00:07:16,680 --> 00:07:18,070
and the herbs she carried

139
00:07:18,360 --> 00:07:19,950
were seized by the guards at the gate.

140
00:07:20,510 --> 00:07:22,360
Experienced guard recognized

141
00:07:22,800 --> 00:07:24,000
that these herbs

142
00:07:24,560 --> 00:07:26,360
are for treating smallpox!

143
00:07:28,360 --> 00:07:29,200
Your Ladyship,

144
00:07:29,360 --> 00:07:32,160
now even Consort Duan is infected.

145
00:07:32,800 --> 00:07:35,870
Does that mean the palace
is not safe anymore?

146
00:07:36,190 --> 00:07:37,310
Your Ladyship,

147
00:07:37,480 --> 00:07:39,040
what should we do?

148
00:07:45,120 --> 00:07:45,960
What to do?

149
00:07:46,390 --> 00:07:47,390
You ask me what to do?

150
00:07:47,600 --> 00:07:48,800
As the Chief Eunuch,

151
00:07:48,920 --> 00:07:50,680
you knew nothing about
smallpox in the palace!

152
00:07:50,950 --> 00:07:52,800
I'm justified in punishing you!

153
00:07:53,720 --> 00:07:54,560
I deserve to die!

154
00:07:54,560 --> 00:07:55,510
I deserve to die.

155
00:07:56,310 --> 00:07:57,160
Deliver my order.

156
00:07:58,390 --> 00:07:59,230
Lock the palace at once.

157
00:07:59,330 --> 00:08:00,750
(Diligent and Virtuous)
Summon physicians for emergency consult.

158
00:08:01,200 --> 00:08:03,310
All concubines and palace staff
who contacted Consort Duan

159
00:08:03,510 --> 00:08:04,720
shall be quarantined.

160
00:08:04,720 --> 00:08:06,000
Yes, Your Majesty.

161
00:08:06,000 --> 00:08:08,980
(Ningshou Palace)

162
00:08:09,630 --> 00:08:10,470
Lock the gate.

163
00:08:13,510 --> 00:08:14,950
Your Ladyship, something is wrong!

164
00:08:15,160 --> 00:08:16,680
Our palace is locked down.

165
00:08:17,040 --> 00:08:18,120
What?

166
00:08:24,830 --> 00:08:26,070
What are you doing?

167
00:08:26,560 --> 00:08:27,870
Stop! Now!

168
00:08:31,920 --> 00:08:33,750
You cannot treat me like this!

169
00:08:33,750 --> 00:08:34,700
(Ningshou Palace)

170
00:08:35,150 --> 00:08:36,720
I want to see His Majesty!

171
00:08:37,080 --> 00:08:39,200
I want to see the Empress Dowager!

172
00:08:40,000 --> 00:08:41,510
Open the door!

173
00:08:42,030 --> 00:08:43,510
Open the door for me!

174
00:08:44,960 --> 00:08:46,360
(Ningshou Palace)
Open the door!

175
00:08:47,120 --> 00:08:47,960
Open the door.

176
00:08:58,120 --> 00:08:59,080
My child,

177
00:09:01,360 --> 00:09:03,480
I'm sorry for you.

178
00:09:07,320 --> 00:09:10,240
Why did I get smallpox?

179
00:09:13,120 --> 00:09:14,750
I stayed indoors

180
00:09:15,910 --> 00:09:17,360
to nurture the baby.

181
00:09:20,440 --> 00:09:22,910
What on earth went wrong?

182
00:09:25,720 --> 00:09:27,720
How could this happen?

183
00:09:30,600 --> 00:09:31,630
Greetings, Your Ladyship.

184
00:09:34,630 --> 00:09:36,000
The new fabric for this year

185
00:09:36,320 --> 00:09:38,080
has already been delivered, hasn't it?

186
00:09:38,600 --> 00:09:39,910
Why is there so much more?

187
00:09:40,030 --> 00:09:41,440
This is this year's tribute.

188
00:09:41,510 --> 00:09:43,120
This fabric doesn't keep well.

189
00:09:43,240 --> 00:09:44,720
His Majesty ordered it
to be sent to the harem

190
00:09:44,790 --> 00:09:46,630
and distributed to all consorts.

191
00:09:46,720 --> 00:09:48,790
I brought it to you, Your Ladyship.

192
00:09:48,790 --> 00:09:50,670
And delivered it here to you.

193
00:09:53,910 --> 00:09:56,630
This fabric is soft and elegant.

194
00:09:56,700 --> 00:09:58,030
It's suitable for making nightgowns.

195
00:09:58,790 --> 00:09:59,670
Zhen'er,

196
00:10:00,080 --> 00:10:02,390
go make several nightgowns for me.

197
00:10:02,390 --> 00:10:03,320
Yes.

198
00:10:19,750 --> 00:10:20,590
The fabric...

199
00:10:21,440 --> 00:10:23,080
There's something wrong with the fabric!

200
00:10:26,720 --> 00:10:30,600
Why did the eunuch of
the Imperial Household harm me?

201
00:10:34,120 --> 00:10:34,960
It was her.

202
00:10:36,150 --> 00:10:37,790
She has run the palace for years.

203
00:10:38,030 --> 00:10:40,360
She must have ordered someone to do it!

204
00:10:44,000 --> 00:10:44,840
It must be her.

205
00:10:47,670 --> 00:10:49,150
I'm going to expose her.

206
00:10:50,960 --> 00:10:52,390
- Consort Lan!
- Your Ladyship.

207
00:10:52,750 --> 00:10:54,150
It's Consort Lan!

208
00:10:54,600 --> 00:10:55,550
Your Majesty,

209
00:10:55,870 --> 00:10:57,870
you've been troubled
by the plague recently,

210
00:10:57,960 --> 00:10:59,480
please don't overwork yourself,

211
00:10:59,480 --> 00:11:00,600
or you'll harm your health.

212
00:11:00,600 --> 00:11:01,790
Mother, don't worry.

213
00:11:02,150 --> 00:11:04,390
I have ordered the Imperial Clinic
to do their best to treat the sick.

214
00:11:04,750 --> 00:11:06,510
I believe there will be results soon.

215
00:11:06,960 --> 00:11:08,720
Mm. That's good, then.

216
00:11:08,960 --> 00:11:09,910
Your Majesty,

217
00:11:10,270 --> 00:11:11,110
Empress Dowager,

218
00:11:12,080 --> 00:11:15,120
Consort Duan has refused to
be confined in her palace,

219
00:11:15,510 --> 00:11:17,200
and even caused a big scene.

220
00:11:17,480 --> 00:11:18,440
It is said...

221
00:11:18,440 --> 00:11:19,720
Stop hesitating,

222
00:11:19,910 --> 00:11:20,790
speak your mind.

223
00:11:21,120 --> 00:11:22,200
I daren't say.

224
00:11:24,390 --> 00:11:26,720
Consort Duan says her smallpox infection

225
00:11:26,720 --> 00:11:28,270
was a setup by Consort Lan,

226
00:11:28,550 --> 00:11:31,320
and she has been
cursing Consort Lan because of this.

227
00:11:32,000 --> 00:11:32,910
At a time like this,

228
00:11:32,910 --> 00:11:34,000
she is still fighting for favor?

229
00:11:34,390 --> 00:11:35,510
It's ridiculous!

230
00:11:37,550 --> 00:11:40,670
That child seems gentle on weekdays,

231
00:11:41,080 --> 00:11:43,600
why does she lose her sense in a crisis?

232
00:11:44,600 --> 00:11:46,750
The source of the plague
hasn't been found yet,

233
00:11:46,750 --> 00:11:48,080
and everyone is panicked.

234
00:11:48,510 --> 00:11:50,390
Her shouting and causing trouble now

235
00:11:51,120 --> 00:11:52,790
will only stir up chaos.

236
00:11:59,480 --> 00:12:00,320
Empress Dowager,

237
00:12:00,390 --> 00:12:01,320
Consort Lan asks for an audience.

238
00:12:02,550 --> 00:12:03,960
At this critical moment,

239
00:12:03,960 --> 00:12:06,270
why isn't she staying in her own palace?

240
00:12:06,510 --> 00:12:08,080
What is she doing coming to see me?

241
00:12:08,600 --> 00:12:11,240
She says it's about the smallpox.

242
00:12:12,150 --> 00:12:12,990
Fine,

243
00:12:13,390 --> 00:12:14,480
let her in.

244
00:12:16,360 --> 00:12:19,390
Let's see what trouble
she's stirring up this time.

245
00:12:25,030 --> 00:12:27,000
Greetings, Your Majesty,

246
00:12:27,150 --> 00:12:28,270
Empress Dowager.

247
00:12:29,320 --> 00:12:30,270
Rise.

248
00:12:30,270 --> 00:12:31,200
Thank you, Empress Dowager.

249
00:12:32,960 --> 00:12:34,960
Why have you come to the Cining Palace?

250
00:12:35,390 --> 00:12:36,390
Your Majesty,

251
00:12:36,870 --> 00:12:39,600
I have been worried and anxious

252
00:12:39,600 --> 00:12:41,720
ever since smallpox
appeared in the capital.

253
00:12:42,120 --> 00:12:45,240
So I asked my father and brother
to seek folk prescriptions.

254
00:12:45,720 --> 00:12:48,200
Although we haven't found
a cure for smallpox,

255
00:12:48,480 --> 00:12:50,270
we found an ancient prescription

256
00:12:50,390 --> 00:12:51,750
that can prevent the disease

257
00:12:51,790 --> 00:12:52,750
and may

258
00:12:52,960 --> 00:12:53,870
slow its spread.

259
00:12:54,870 --> 00:12:58,750
I humbly offer this formula
to Your Majesty.

260
00:13:04,140 --> 00:13:06,700
(Smallpox Prescription)

261
00:13:11,740 --> 00:13:12,960
Consort Lan cares about the state

262
00:13:13,240 --> 00:13:14,230
and shows care for everyone.

263
00:13:14,720 --> 00:13:15,560
That is truly rare.

264
00:13:18,150 --> 00:13:19,510
Consort Duan has an epidemic

265
00:13:19,870 --> 00:13:20,870
and is pregnant.

266
00:13:21,550 --> 00:13:23,600
She is now at the center of turmoil.

267
00:13:23,790 --> 00:13:26,120
The harem cannot be
without a leader for a day.

268
00:13:26,790 --> 00:13:28,600
I intend to promote you
to Noble Consort,

269
00:13:29,000 --> 00:13:31,510
and let you temporarily
manage the harem affairs.

270
00:13:31,800 --> 00:13:33,000
Are you willing to bear this duty?

271
00:13:40,870 --> 00:13:42,270
I'm honored.

272
00:13:42,390 --> 00:13:45,670
I only wish to share Your Majesty's
worries with my humble efforts.

273
00:13:50,270 --> 00:13:51,870
What is your opinion, mother?

274
00:13:52,320 --> 00:13:55,080
Since Your Majesty
has made up your mind,

275
00:13:55,630 --> 00:13:57,270
why ask me?

276
00:14:00,390 --> 00:14:01,360
Get out!

277
00:14:01,720 --> 00:14:03,080
- Get out of my sight!
- Your Highness.

278
00:14:04,390 --> 00:14:05,600
Go, go, go.

279
00:14:09,440 --> 00:14:10,510
What's wrong?

280
00:14:12,080 --> 00:14:14,150
(The 14th Prince
rarely appears in the novel.)

281
00:14:14,150 --> 00:14:16,360
(He never showed up
during the smallpox incident.)

282
00:14:16,390 --> 00:14:18,270
(I didn't expect it would affect him.)

283
00:14:18,870 --> 00:14:19,710
Stay back.

284
00:14:25,670 --> 00:14:26,510
Let me see.

285
00:14:27,550 --> 00:14:28,870
Eunuch Fu was right.

286
00:14:30,790 --> 00:14:31,960
So you really were infected.

287
00:14:33,600 --> 00:14:34,480
Now that you know,

288
00:14:36,570 --> 00:14:37,840
why don't you stay away from me?

289
00:14:38,150 --> 00:14:39,480
We stay together every day.

290
00:14:39,670 --> 00:14:41,630
Isn't it too late to stay away now?

291
00:14:53,610 --> 00:14:56,050
♪I am but an outsider♪

292
00:14:56,090 --> 00:14:58,250
♪Yet something drags me deeper♪

293
00:14:58,490 --> 00:15:02,530
♪Outwit the world
but not the way we meet♪

294
00:15:02,530 --> 00:15:06,770
♪Splendid blooms line deadly ground♪

295
00:15:11,050 --> 00:15:14,290
♪Life's a phantom, yet I find you♪

296
00:15:14,450 --> 00:15:17,850
♪In a world of lies,
you're all that's clear♪

297
00:15:17,850 --> 00:15:20,370
♪I know how this story ends♪

298
00:15:20,370 --> 00:15:24,930
♪I still want what's in your eyes♪

299
00:15:25,250 --> 00:15:29,370
♪Truth or lie—I can't tell♪

300
00:15:34,330 --> 00:15:37,650
♪You hide it all behind your lines♪

301
00:15:37,650 --> 00:15:40,930
♪So familiar, yet out of reach♪

302
00:15:41,130 --> 00:15:44,210
♪A history that no one can search♪

303
00:15:44,450 --> 00:15:47,730
♪Like you drift in from another star♪

304
00:15:47,770 --> 00:15:49,530
♪I am but an outsider♪

305
00:15:49,530 --> 00:15:51,770
♪Yet something drags me deeper♪

306
00:15:51,770 --> 00:15:55,810
♪Outwit the world
but not the way we meet♪

307
00:15:55,810 --> 00:16:00,490
♪Splendid blooms line deadly ground♪

308
00:16:04,410 --> 00:16:07,810
♪Life's a phantom, yet I find you♪

309
00:16:07,810 --> 00:16:11,170
♪In a world of lies,
you're all that's clear♪

310
00:16:11,170 --> 00:16:13,650
♪I know how this story ends♪

311
00:16:13,650 --> 00:16:17,810
♪I still want what's in your eyes♪

312
00:16:17,810 --> 00:16:21,090
♪When it's over and I'm gone♪

313
00:16:21,090 --> 00:16:24,890
♪Please forget me and move on♪

314
00:16:24,890 --> 00:16:31,130
♪Just let this absurd dream fade♪

315
00:16:34,290 --> 00:16:42,650
♪Snow hides our tracks♪

316
00:16:46,210 --> 00:16:55,930
♪When do I finally wake♪
